title: Oollalla Oollalla
overview: Pandu (Nataraj) is an aspiring film director who studies engineering. Noorin (Noorin Shereef) is from the same college and falls in love with him for no reason. When Pandu gets lost in a forest and reaches a haunted mansion, how Trisha (Ankeeta Maharana) seduces him is what it's all about.
